findings.title: Out of gas
findings.description: The functions includeInReward() and _getCurrentSupply() use loops to find and remove addresses from the _excluded list and evaluate total supply respectively, which can lead to OUT_OF_GAS exceptions if there are long excluded addresses lists.

findings.title: Owner privileges (In the period when the owner is not renounced)
findings.description: The contract owner has excessive privileges to change various parameters and settings when the ownership is not renounced.
